    {"type":"text","id":"ll_sub","x":10,"y":64,"width":270,"height":14,"text":"Left-to-right, Leftmost derivation, 1 lookahead","originalText":"Left-to-right, Leftmost derivation, 1 lookahead","fontSize":10,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#065f46","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":15,"version":1,"versionNonce":16,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25},
    {"type":"text","id":"ll_c","x":18,"y":84,"width":254,"height":144,"text":"Dirección: TOP-DOWN (raíz → hojas)\nEstrategia: Mira 1 token adelante\nImplementación: Recursión descendente\n   (código a mano, fácil de leer)\n\n✓ Fácil de escribir y mantener\n✓ Buenos mensajes de error\n✗ NO maneja recursión izquierda\n   expr → expr + term  ← INFINITO\n✗ Gramaticas limitadas\n\nTool: parsers hechos a mano\nEjemplo XGrammar: NO (usa Earley)","originalText":"Dirección: TOP-DOWN (raíz → hojas)\nEstrategia: Mira 1 token adelante\nImplementación: Recursión descendente\n   (código a mano, fácil de leer)\n\n✓ Fácil de escribir y mantener\n✓ Buenos mensajes de error\n✗ NO maneja recursión izquierda\n   expr → expr + term  ← INFINITO\n✗ Gramaticas limitadas\n\nTool: parsers hechos a mano\nEjemplo XGrammar: NO (usa Earley)","fontSize":11,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#065f46","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":17,"version":1,"versionNonce":18,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.4},

