    {"type":"text","id":"earley_h","x":590,"y":44,"width":300,"height":18,"text":"Earley Parsing","originalText":"Earley Parsing","fontSize":15,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#92400e","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":33,"version":1,"versionNonce":34,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25},
    {"type":"text","id":"earley_sub","x":590,"y":64,"width":300,"height":14,"text":"Algoritmo dinámico — acepta CUALQUIER CFG","originalText":"Algoritmo dinámico — acepta CUALQUIER CFG","fontSize":10,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#92400e","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":35,"version":1,"versionNonce":36,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25},
    {"type":"text","id":"earley_c","x":598,"y":84,"width":284,"height":144,"text":"Dirección: TOP-DOWN con programación dinámica\nComplejidad: O(n³) caso general, O(n) para la mayoría\nIdea: \"Ítems Earley\" — hipótesis parciales de parse\n\n✓ Acepta CUALQUIER CFG sin modificarla\n✓ Gramáticas ambiguas son OK (reporta todas)\n✓ Gramáticas con recursión izquierda OK\n✓ Ideal para lenguajes constraint/DSL\n✗ Más lento que LL/LR para gram. simples\n\nTool: implementación propia, lark, nearley\n★ XGrammar usa Earley → acepta EBNF\n   arbitraria sin reformularla","originalText":"Dirección: TOP-DOWN con programación dinámica\nComplejidad: O(n³) caso general, O(n) para la mayoría\nIdea: \"Ítems Earley\" — hipótesis parciales de parse\n\n✓ Acepta CUALQUIER CFG sin modificarla\n✓ Gramáticas ambiguas son OK (reporta todas)\n✓ Gramáticas con recursión izquierda OK\n✓ Ideal para lenguajes constraint/DSL\n✗ Más lento que LL/LR para gram. simples\n\nTool: implementación propia, lark, nearley\n★ XGrammar usa Earley → acepta EBNF\n   arbitraria sin reformularla","fontSize":11,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#92400e","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":37,"version":1,"versionNonce":38,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.4},

